(18, 'applgo443', 30184300, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:28:28', 'This is really cool!<p>I have a few questions<p>1. Is there really no other competitor or company that tried to tackle this problem in the past? It feels like a really common usecase and someone must&#x27;ve done something about it!<p>2. Do you have a fixed set of words that the user should use to query? I&#x27;m an AI researcher&#x2F;practitioner who worked in this area. It&#x27;s super difficult to search for tail objects in images&#x2F;text.<p>3. Why API first?', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30181676, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
