(22, 'huitzitziltzin', 30184304, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:28:43', 'Straightforward antitrust violation.  This is exactly what they got in trouble w&#x2F; in the 1990&#x27;s w.r.t. bundling IE w&#x2F; Windows.   But they know exactly what they are doing.  They aren&#x27;t unaware of the fact that this a violation.<p>There is a lot of complaining on this site about various FAANG members&#x27; anticompetitive behavior (some of it uninformed!), but you all need to make room in your hearts for an M in that acronym when you&#x27;re talking about antitrust issues, because this behavior is anticompetitive.', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30180861, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
