(33, 'holdenk', 30184315, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:29:28', 'So they don&#x27;t do dedicated boxes (sadly), they rent by the rack (including 1gb of transit + 15A power). <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;he.net&#x2F;colocation.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;he.net&#x2F;colocation.html</a> has the info. If you just want a dedicated box that isn&#x27;t drawing a lot of power I&#x27;ve probably got some room in my rack and we can chat (and I imagine some of the other BGP for fun group folks are in similar positions).', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30183696, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
