(37, 'swyx', 30184319, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:29:41', 'i mean, have some sympathy, easy to criticize from the cheap seats. (and yes, they are paid a lot, so what, decisionmaking under uncertainty is still hard)<p>in retrospect, LHL distancing himself from covid policy is pretty brilliant&#x2F;convenient, as whoever proves a credible leader through this mess will have demonstrated the qualities we&#x27;d probably want for PM', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30179002, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
