(76, 'jacquesm', 30184358, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:33:22', 'I can see where the reference comes from, there isn&#x27;t all that much to pick if you want to use a color:<p><a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;abcnews.go.com&#x2F;International&#x2F;north-koreas-parade-bigger-twist-reporters-notebook&#x2F;story?id=57672421\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;abcnews.go.com&#x2F;International&#x2F;north-koreas-parade-big...</a>', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30183303, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
