(94, 'hnthrowaway0315', 30184376, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:34:33', 'Second thought, if one wants to develop DOOM as Carmack did, he would need a NeXT workstation, might not be easy to come by TBH, but maybe there is am emulator good enough.', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30184094, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
