(96, 'scoot', 30184378, NULL, '2022-02-02 22:35:03', 'Isn&#x27;t the distribution of the stopping force over a larger surface area also a factor in reducing the impact?<p>That said, I&#x27;ve no idea what the benefit of this material would be for this application, or why GP felt the need to suggest it when it&#x27;s mentioned in the very  first paragraph of the article.', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30183972, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
