(274, 'throwaway81523', 30189653, NULL, '2022-02-03 08:19:06', 'Right, I&#x27;ll usually do an initial phone consultation for free, but anything more expensive would be billed.  The issue is that there is not usually a well-defined problem.  There is a general goal that takes some iterations to accomplish, with the customer concocting new features and requirements as development progresses.  Of course everyone says to build some padding into the schedule for that, but they think of expansion factors like 10% when it really has to be 10x.<p>If it really is a well defined, contained problem, they will probably go on Fiver since they don&#x27;t really need any design help, which is the most useful thing I can usually supply as a consultant.  Banging out code is by itself nothing special these days.', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30189317, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
(275, '_Microft', 30189654, NULL, '2022-02-03 08:19:31', 'Most people cannot, believe that they cannot, or would not even if they could. We can be sure of that because despite of billions of cameras in phones, pocket cameras or webcams being out there, the web is not flooded by pictures like these.\nPutting filters into cameras definitely works. It is not an obstacle to the determined but it prevents most of the abuse most of the time.', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30183064, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
