(396, 'sudosysgen', 30196981, NULL, '2022-02-03 19:58:58', 'That is simply false. Few countries hypocritical about counter-intelligence. You absolutely have to draw the difference between intelligence work and counter-intelligence work. Saying that going after someone for catching your spies is normal is totally insane, no one except the US does it.<p>If Uganda was spying on the US in the US, then you would have a point. That&#x27;s not what happened.', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30196229, 'None', NULL, NULL, 0),
