(594, 'elldoubleyew', 30197178, NULL, '2022-02-03 20:10:12', 'I’ve always wondered if I have a “gaming addiction”<p>I play league of legends at least 4 hours per day, sometimes 20+ hours. I am obsessed with learning all the intricacies and improving in the ELO-based ranking system.<p>I still maintain a full time job as an SWE, a romantic relationship, and personal hygiene&#x2F;diet. Admittedly LoL comes first before work for me, and can cause tension in my relationship at times.<p>I know many men that have a very similar relationship with golf, but are they golf addicts?', 'comment', NULL, NULL, NULL, 30197037, '[30197291]', NULL, NULL, 0),
